title: Ebro In The Morning - Just One Of Those Days.
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 9/24.

Ebro and the crew talk about some exclusive Fugees music (36), as well as the recent Haitian migration (1). Laura Stylez has her patented Flashing Lights segments at minutes 11, & 33. 

Please like and subscribe to Ebro In The Morning.
